data.description: Accepted contract, on the market for back up offers pending contingency release. This beautiful home is everything you have been hoping for plus minutes from everywhere you want to be! You are going to love the newly updated kitchen w/ stainless appliances, painted cabinetry, new backsplash, kitchen counters & sink. Other features are soaring ceilings in the main living area, dedicated dining room, gorgeous flooring through the main living area, newly painted living room & bedrooms, a bonus/flex room on the main floor can be used for an extra family room or office area, updated bathroom w/ new flooring, vanity and toilet.  The primary bedroom features trayed ceiling & the ensuite bathroom has a new tiled shower and updated fixtures and flooring. The downstairs has a gorgeous, bricked fireplace and is waiting for the new owner to make it theirs! Summer is around the corner & you are going to love the huge back yard with mature trees, & a large storage shed.
